OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F: First minister faces     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSenedd questions for final 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftime - BBC News            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, One of Mark Drakeford's last tasks as  
OL,6, first minister will be taking a final  
OL,7, round of questions from opposition     
OL,8, leaders in the Senedd.                 
OL,10,FHe will then submit a resignation      
OL,11,Fletter, before formally offering his   
OL,12,Fresignation to the King later on.      
OL,14,FOn Wednesday, he will be replaced in   
OL,15,Fthe role by Vaughan Gething.           
OL,17,FGood afternoon and welcome to our live 
OL,18,Fcoverage of the last day in office for 
OL,19,FWales' First Minister Mark Drakeford,  
OL,20,Fthe most high profile politician in    
OL,21,FWales since devolution in 1999.        
